<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-80-1068 </DOCNO><TEXT>The 1980 eruption of St.Helens, U.S.A. has attracted attention becauseits mode of action is similar to that of Bandai volcano. Authors havereinvestigated the eruptive activity of the Bandai volcano of 1888 whichhas been regarded as a non-magma eruption. This report summarizes onthe characteristics and mechanism of especially explosive steam typeeruption, the debris-avalanche and the blast, and a series of eruptiveactivities by comparing with the 1980 eruption of the St.Helens volcano.(4 figs, 2 tabs, 21 refs)</TEXT></DOC>